    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A geophysical technique of surveying involving the measurement of the resistance of the earth to an electric current passing between metal electrodes; used in archaeology especially to locate buried remains.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000008431/Champion, Dictionary of Terms and Techniques in Archaeology (1980)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Técnica geofísica de agrimensura que involucra la medida de la resistencia de la tierra a una corriente eléctrica que pasa entre electrodos metálicos; usado en arqueología especialmente para localizar restos enterrados.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Een geofysische overzichtstechniek waarbij de weerstand  wordt gemeten van de aarde tegen een elektrische stroom die door metalen elektroden wordt geleid; wordt met name gebruikt in de archeologie om begraven overblijfselen te lokaliseren.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
    </Descriptive_Notes>
